---
// Founder/About Guruji Section
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-purple-50 to-spiritual/5 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative Elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-gold/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-spiritual bg-clip-text text-transparent">Meet Our Guruji</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        {/* Image Section */}
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-spiritual rounded-3xl opacity-20 animate-pulse-slow"></div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-accent rounded-3xl opacity-15 animate-pulse-slow" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
            <img 
              src="/assets/images/nadi/mem2.jpg" 
              alt="Guruji Thillaimani" 
              class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-spiritual w-full h-auto border-4 border-gold/30"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Content Section */}
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">Guruji Thillaimani</h3>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            With over 25 years of dedicated experience in the sacred tradition of Nadi Astrology, Guruji Thillaimani has guided thousands of seekers from around the world on their spiritual journey.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Born and raised in Vaitheeswaran Koil, the epicenter of Nadi Astrology, Guruji inherited this divine knowledge through a lineage of authentic Nadi readers. His profound understanding of ancient palm leaves and dedication to preserving this sacred tradition has made him one of the most trusted names in Sree Agasthiya Maha Siva Nadi Astrology.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
            My mission is simple and heartfelt: to provide you access to authentic Nadi Astrology readings and support you in discovering guidance, purpose, and a stronger connection to your life's path. Every reading is conducted with utmost care, ensuring accuracy and spiritual integrity.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl shadow-spiritual mb-8 border border-primary/20">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-5 text-primary">Why Choose Guruji Thillaimani?</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 text-lg">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-gold mr-3 font-bold text-2xl">✓</span>
                <span>25+ years of authentic Nadi reading experience</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-gold mr-3 font-bold text-2xl">✓</span>
                <span>Direct lineage from Vaitheeswaran Koil tradition</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-gold mr-3 font-bold text-2xl">✓</span>
                <span>Served 10,000+ clients worldwide</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-gold mr-3 font-bold text-2xl">✓</span>
                <span>Expert in multiple Nadi texts (Agasthiya, Siva, Bhrigu, etc.)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-gold mr-3 font-bold text-2xl">✓</span>
                <span>Available for online and in-person consultations</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <a href="/guruji-thillaimani" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-spiritual text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-spiritual transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl">
            Read Full Biography
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
